children.text: Enough Said spoken word event series event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on May 1, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Ian Stephens, Lynn Suderman, Ann Diamond, and Justin McGrail. No supporting or open mic performers.
